<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">The interval for transitions between items.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">
<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Transition type</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59"><strong sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Slide</strong> or <strong sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">Fade</strong></td>
<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">The transition effect between items.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">
<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">Hide carousel flipper</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60"><strong sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">True</strong> or <strong sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">False</strong></td>
<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">If the value is set to <strong sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">True</strong>, the carousel flipper and sequence indicator are hidden.</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">
