<td sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">If the value is set to <strong sourcefile="articles/commerce/add-carousel.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">True</strong>, users can dismiss the carousel.</td>
</tr>
